correctness.rationale: Largely incorrect and weakly grounded to the article with multiple schema and factual issues. Key problems: (1) Missing multiple processes: the article reports three IGZO ALD compositions (A, B, C) with subcycle ratios 0:2:2, 1:2:2, 2:2:2, but only one process is extracted, violating the multi-process requirement. (2) Supercycle design incorrect: numberofSubcycles should reflect TEIn:In-Ga:DEZn counts for A/B/C; instead a single count for “InGaZnO” is given and subcycle ratios are not captured. (3) Many parameters are fabricated/not reported: pressure (10 mTorr), dosingTime (100 ms), purgeTime (100 ms), flowRates (10 sccm/100 sccm), saturation=True, nucleationPeriod=5 cycles, carrierGas=N2 (carrier gas not stated), uniformity (5%), conformality aspect ratio (10), roughness (1.2 nm), film density (5.5 g/dm3), refractive index (1.8), absorption coefficient (0.01), band gap (3.0 eV), resistivity (0.001 Ω·m), carrier density (1e19), Hall measurements—none of these are in the paper. (4) Schema issues: plasmaPower is set to null (type mismatch; should be omitted for TALD), device subthresholdSwing uses 0.29 mV instead of 0.29 V/dec reported in Table 3 (should be ~290 mV/dec if using mV units), growthPerCycle entries are mislabeled under compound “InGaZnO” instead of per-precursor (TEIn 0.67 Å/cycle, In–Ga bimetallic 0.44 Å/cycle, DEZn 0.65 Å/cycle). (5) numberofCycles=20 is incorrect/ungrounded (paper specifies 20 nm film thickness, not total cycles). (6) Film composition is inconsistently reported: atomicRatio ‘0.7:1.0:1.8’ (Film B) is correct from Table 2, but elemental concentration is given as a single 20.1% value without mapping to all elements. (7) Device metrics are partially correct only for BOA (μ=12.9 cm^2/V·s, VTH=3.7 V) but SS unit is wrong; on/off ratio 1e7 is not reported. (8) Several fields (safety, reproducibility, film stability) are generic guesses, not traceable. Corrections needed: extract three separate processes (A, B, C) with correct supercycle subcycle counts (TEIn:In-Ga:DEZn = 0:2:2; 1:2:2; 2:2:2), remove unreported parameters (pressure, times, flows, etc.) or mark as not provided, fix SS to 0.29 V/dec (~290 mV), attribute GPC values to the correct precursors, omit plasmaPower for TALD, ensure composition fields reflect full In:Ga:Zn at.% from Table 2, and limit device metrics to those reported (Table 3).

completeness.rationale: Largely incomplete and often untraceable to the article, with schema issues. Key issues: (1) Multiple processes not captured: the article reports three IGZO ALD compositions (A, B, C) with distinct supercycle ratios (TEIn:In-Ga:DEZn = 0:2:2, 1:2:2, 2:2:2) and multiple gate-stack/device variants (OI, OA, HA, HI). Only a single process is extracted; supercycleDesign does not encode the per-composition subcycle counts. (2) Many parameters are fabricated and not reported in the paper: reactor pressure (10 mTorr), numberofCycles (20), dosing/purge times (100 ms), flow rates (10/100 sccm), nucleationPeriod (5 cycles), saturation, optical properties (n, absorption, band gap), uniformity, conformality, resistivity, carrier density, Hall mobility, roughness, film density, on/off ratio, safety, filmStability, reproducibility. These values are not traceable to the text and should be removed or supported. (3) Schema violations/inconsistencies: plasmaPower is set to null (should be omitted for TALD); subthresholdSwing uses unit MilliV for a value of 0.29 (should be 290 mV or 0.29 V/dec); filmComposition.elementalConcentration provides a single percent without specifying elements (Table 2 provides In/Ga/Zn at.% that should be captured per element); growthPerCycle is labeled under 'InGaZnO' rather than per precursor (TEIn 0.67 Å/cycle, In-Ga bimetallic 0.44 Å/cycle, DEZn 0.65 Å/cycle); supercycleDesign numberofSubcycles is incomplete (should list counts per subcycle for each composition); several device metrics correspond to BOA but the extraction does not specify the process context. (4) Partial alignments: temperature 200 °C, substrate SiO2/Si, carrier/purging gas N2, oxidant O3, film thickness 20 nm, device structure TGBC are correct. To be complete and schema-compliant, add separate process instances for films A, B, and C with correct supercycle counts and corresponding device properties (e.g., AOI/BOI/COI, AOA/BOA/COA, AHA/BHA/CHA), fix units (SS in mV/dec), remove or source any unreported parameters (pressure, dosing/purge/flows, film density/roughness/optics/electrical), provide XPS elemental concentrations per element from Table 2, and omit plasmaPower for TALD.
